div1.p:
Q. Was your fellow servant with you? - A. My fellow servant was gone;
Francis Roberts
came to me.

Q. Was it dry or wet? - A.Wet; the gardener asked us if we had seen a man in a smock-frock; we said, no; and then we all got up to see if there was any thing gone; I missed Miss Cole's red spotted gown; and the gardener, and the other servant, went to follow him;
William Goring
brought back the gown to me; the prisoner was brought back with it.
